line_1: Bonds, judgments, executions, ope their paws;
line_2: Behold her now in Ruin's frightful jaws!

line_1: For thee the Bear retracts his shaggy paws;
line_2: For thee Cassiope her chair withdraws,

line_1: She wags her tail, protends her paws;
line_2: Near and more near Grimalkin draws,

line_1: When farthest, as she deem'd, from paws;
line_2: For why? she oft has felt their claws,
